## Dependencies I Used

```xml
<!-- BCrypt hashing -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>at.favre.lib</groupId>
    <artifactId>bcrypt</artifactId>
    <version>0.9.0</version>
</dependency>

<!-- SQLite JDBC -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.xerial</groupId>
    <artifactId>sqlite-jdbc</artifactId>
    <version>3.45.1.0</version>
</dependency>
```

AES-256-CBC encryption uses the standard **JCE** bundled with the JDK — no extra dependency needed.

